# ⚠️ Important Notes

## 1. High performance is expected

Because:

* rule-based target
* structured survey variables
* strong proxy features

---

## 2. Model is NOT purely causal

This is:

> predictive proxy modeling, not causal inference

---

## 3. Feature space is still high-dimensional

Even after reduction:

* 604 features = high-dimensional logistic regression

---

